{"tid":199140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[GEOG衝5**專區] 試前討論區","createTime":"2017-04-13T03:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T12:51:44.000Z","uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4126cd3dae7f6021ba6c824e22dcb83ba460fb31","tid":199140,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:39:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">地理最重要:技巧。</span><br />\n點樣有系統快速背書、點樣答問題、點樣善用剩底時間、以最有限時間讀最多的野，呢啲都係幫你攞高分的重要技巧。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n有巴打問:<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我三年黎校冇考試冇合格過 但上次個Mock 岩岩2左 我有冇可能攞到5**<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n巴打 有幾個概念比番你：<br />\n<br />\n1. 只要你相信自己，盡力，無悔，你5**與否都係聽天由命。信心一定要 keep 住！<br />\n<br />\n2. MOCK 只供參考，唔少學生的MOCK不堪入目，但出黎成績同樣可以璀璨奪目<br />\n<br />\n3. 你瞄5* 會比5**更現實，5*同5**我相信係運氣問題，而且5*同5**對升讀非神科的幫助差唔多<br />\n<br />\n4. 最緊要係技巧。點樣有系統快速背書、點樣答問題、點樣善用剩底時間、以最有限時間讀最多的野，呢啲都係幫你攞高分的重要技巧。 <br />\n<br />\n免費essay評語   歡迎telegram <a href=\"http://t.me/Scottish_Salmon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FScottish_Salmon&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4cVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=2bbf69c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/Scottish_Salmon</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4dbcc9702e9db7f44cefe7a2dc33dbdda386bb","tid":199140,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9bb2d89cea8ef44884428e255029531081a369","tid":199140,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbb0d66c30359b7bb4af70cb3028a53f72e7c32","tid":199140,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"